[*] PRE-CONFERENCE CTF

This year the CTF is going to be run by Bonsai-sec & Netifera as a  
warm-up the setup a 3 day CTF
The pre-conference CTF game starts on Aug 17, 13:37 and ends Aug 21  
13:37 (GMT-3).
More information: http://ctf.ekoparty.org

